<body>
The money system here contains four types of coins:<br>
Copper<br>
Silver = 10 copper<br>
Gold = 10 silver<br>
Platinum = 10 gold<br>
<br>
In order to give coins to another pc, type:<br>
give [number_of_coins]*[coin_type] [pc_name]<br>
eg, give 3*gold greyclaw<br>
<br>
To drop coins, simply type:<br>
drop [number_of_coins]*[coin_type]<br>
 eg, drop 2*copper<br>
<br>
Note: using the abbreviations: cp, sp, gp, pp, will not work.<br>
<br>
Other help files that may be useful include help Bank.<br>
